project_descr: In 2018, with a new Parliament in place, which is more diverse and representative,  the project will push for a more strengthened parliamentary framework  to improve  law making, representation and oversight and thereby good governance in the country.

outputs.output_descr: A new Parliamentary Service Commission consisting of the different political parties represented in the fifth Parliament will be formed. The PSC as well the new MPs will need to be capacitated in different aspects on parliamentary functioning to enable them to perform their mandated roles.
